Installing trytond_sale_advance_payment
=======================================

Prerequisites
-------------

 * Python 3.4 or later (http://www.python.org/)
 * simpleeval (https://github.com/danthedeckie/simpleeval)
 * trytond (http://www.tryton.org/)
 * trytond_sale (http://www.tryton.org/)
 * trytond_account_invoice (http://www.tryton.org/)

Installation
------------

Once you've downloaded and unpacked the trytond_sale_advance_payment source
release, enter the directory where the archive was unpacked, and run:

    python setup.py install

Note that you may need administrator/root privileges for this step, as
this command will by default attempt to install module to the Python
site-packages directory on your system.

For advance options, please refer to the easy_install and/or the distutils
documentation:

  http://peak.telecommunity.com/DevCenter/EasyInstall
  http://docs.python.org/inst/inst.html

To use without installation, extract the archive into ``trytond/modules`` with
the directory name sale_advance_payment.
